    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014it still runs like a dream and looks great on the road! It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value for someone who wants a dependable vehicle they can count on. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a test drive!",
