    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96/03 flat-six power plant, delivering a linear torque curve thanks to VarioCam Plus valve timing. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the gear engagement is crisp with zero synchro hesitation. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its multi-link rear suspension to manage weight transfer effectively through apexes. Essential preventative maintenance has been performed, including an upgraded IMS bearing and rear main seal, ensuring the integrity of the intermediate shaft. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver's car, the mechanical vitals are exceptional. Four-piston monoblock calipers provide firm, fade-resistant deceleration, and the communicative hydraulic steering rack offers the direct feedback purists crave.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
