    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-loved and looked after. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
